OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly cloudy day with some
OL,6,Fpatchy light rain, mainly in the
OL,7,Fafternoon along Deeside. Drier across
OL,8,FMoray and north Aberdeenshire with a
OL,9,Flittle brightness.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FRemaining cloudy through the
OL,12,Fevening with some patchy light rain
OL,13,Fand the chance of some haar. This
OL,14,Fclearing northeast overnight to become
OL,15,Fdry with some brightness by morning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
