OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA dry start with some
OL,6,Fbrightness. Then outbreaks of rain
OL,7,Fspread east, becoming heavy for a time
OL,8,Flater, before clearing during the
OL,9,Fevening. Breezy for a time in the
OL,10,Fafternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,13,FLargely dry with bright or sunny
OL,14,Fspells on Monday morning, a few
OL,15,Fshowers in the afternoon. Bright or
OL,16,Fsunny spells and scattered showers
OL,17,FTuesday and Wednesday, some heavy and
OL,18,Fthundery.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
